Hope you are doing good,

This is Saravanan from Info Way Solutions, LLC We have job opening for

PYTHON DEVELOPER and the detailed Job description is given below:

Kindly check the JD and share your views

Python developer

Maryland (Remote)

Responsibilities/Job Description

  • Design, plan, and develop data driven applications
  • Design, plan, and develop data processing functionality
  • Write python code for AWS services like Glue, EMR, SageMaker, and other technologies for large data processing jobs
  • Identify, research, and create standards and standards documentation
  • Provide demos and training to EAD staff to facilitate forward progress in the adoption of new technologies and new standards

Please list a few tasks that will need to be completed as soon as the personnel starts:

  • Develop a Proof of Concept in SageMaker to replace or enhance the legacy application
  • Reimplement legacy data processing code in SAS and other languages into python
  • Create custom and reusable pip plugins for Flask and Django to support operations

Experience

Python - 4yrs

  • AWS - 4yrs (certificate preferred)
  • Relational Databases (Postgress, MySQL, Oracle) - 4yrs
  • Backend web development fundamentals (Django, Flask) - 2yrs GV

Thanks & Regards,
